OL,5,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FIt takes a stinger operation to
OL,7,     Fstop a dangerous driver who
OL,8,     Freverse-rammed the cops, but the
OL,9,     Finterceptors are in for a surprise
OL,10,     Fwhen they see who is behind the
OL,11,     Fwheel.
OL,12,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FReality series following
OL,14,     Fhigh-speed police intercept units
OL,15,     Fin West Yorkshire. Duncan pursues
OL,16,     Fa driver treating Wakefield city
OL,17,     Fcentre like his own personal
OL,18,     Fracetrack.
