OL,5,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA workplace accident ends with a
OL,7,     Fman pushed through a sheet of
OL,8,     Fglass, and responders have to
OL,9,     Fhandle the cuts; a stabbing victim
OL,10,     Frisks bleeding out on the street.
OL,11,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,12,     FIn Belfast, a semi-pro boxer is
OL,13,     Frushed to A&E after blacking out
OL,14,     Ffrom heavy blows to the head, with
OL,15,     Ffears of a brain bleed, while an
OL,16,     Felderly patient is rushed in
OL,17,     Fstruggling to breathe.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
