OL,5,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe GPs of Hall Green Health are
OL,7,     Fconstantly surprised by their
OL,8,     Fpatients' resilience and ability
OL,9,     Fto pick themselves up when faced
OL,10,     Fwith life's knockbacks.
OL,11,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,13,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,14,     Funder the microscope. Consultant
OL,15,     FDoctor Sue checks over a gentleman
OL,16,     Ffound unconscious at home.
